Relative colors conversion rules:


Starting color:
#000

Type from background-color && border from parent.background-color:
4 step up

Inputs difference:
1 step up from a.link in background-color and color

Hover states modifier:
2 step up for background-color, color and border

button:active and a:focus:
#777 for border and color
#000 for background-color

Modifier of all rules above for smaller viewports:
1 step up for everything except root.background-color
2 step up for borders


